title: Do It Again
lyrics:
Oh, do it again
I may say no, no, no 
But do it again
My lips just ache 
To have you take the kiss that's waiting for you

You know if you do

You won't regret it, come and get it



Oh, when no one is near

I may cry oh, oh, oh 

But no one will hear



Mama may scold me 

'Cause she told me it was naughty but then

Please do it again

Please do it again



Oh, no one is near



I may cry oh, oh, oh

But no one will hear

Mama may scold me 

'Cause she told me it was naughty but then



Oh, do it again

Please do it again
